      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a parts donor. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and the transmission exhibits significant slipping when shifting into third gear. Externally, there is extensive rust on the lower body panels and the paint is peeling in several large sections. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn seating and a non-functional climate control system. It will require a trailer for transport and a significant investment to return to roadworthy condition.",
