      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This showroom-quality specimen has been meticulously maintained to an uncompromising standard, ensuring it looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every detail, from the flawless finish to the untouched interior, reflects a level of care that is seldom found. For the discerning collector or driver who demands excellence, this vehicle offers peerless quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 48900.0,
